{SECT 0 {EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 57 "restart; with(Linea
rAlgebra): with(DEtools): with(plots):" }}{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 
1 0 57 "f := (x,y) -> - y + x * (mu + x^2 + y^2 - (x^2 + y^2)^2);" }}
{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 39 "g := (x,y) ->   x + y * (mu + x^2 +
 y^2" }{MPLTEXT 1 0 16 " - (x^2 + y^2)^2" }{MPLTEXT 1 0 2 ");" }}
{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 37 "DE1 := diff(x(t),t) = -f(x(t), y(t)
):" }}{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 37 "DE2 := diff(y(t),t) = -g(x(t)
, y(t)):" }}{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 16 "DE  := DE1, DE2;" }}
{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "f*6$I\"xG6\"I\"yGF%F%6$I)operatorGF%I&ar
rowGF%F%,&9%!\"\"*&9$\"\"\",*I#muGF%F/*$F.\"\"#F/*$F+F3F/*$,&F2F/F4F/F
3F,F/F/F%F%F%" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "f*6$I\"xG6\"I\"yGF%F%6$
I)operatorGF%I&arrowGF%F%,&9$\"\"\"*&9%F,,*I#muGF%F,*$F+\"\"#F,*$F.F2F
,*$,&F1F,F3F,F2!\"\"F,F,F%F%F%" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6$/-I%
